data.title: David Mordaunt and Caroline VanEgmond - Marriage Records
data.meta_description: Ancestry.ca has at least 1 marriage record for David Mordaunt and Caroline VanEgmond, among more than 2 marriage records for the surname Mordaunt and more than 27 marriage records for the surname VanEgmond.
data.text:
Ancestry.ca, the largest online family history resource, can help you explore marriage records for David Mordaunt and Caroline VanEgmond from among its billions of historical records from Canada and around the world.

Marriage records are primary resources for the marriage details, since they were created at the time of the marriage. Ancestry.ca collections include indexes that can help you request the record, and in some cases, actual images of the marriage records.
